Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,0)\blur4}一切都重叠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:38.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey 闭嘴 在这等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:40.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur4}在昏暗的房间中独自等待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:43.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey 闭嘴 在这等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:46.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(330,0)\blur4}我听见踢碎房门的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:48.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey 闭嘴 在这等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:51.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(330,0)\blur4}在昏暗的房间中独自等待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:53.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Hey 闭嘴 在这等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:56.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你已无需恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:58.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}提着上膛的步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:01.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}踢破紧锁的坚固大门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:03.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}紧握着枪开火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(100,100)}贯穿了昨日的我
